<collectingRegion box="[1268,1343,367,392]" country="Germany" name="Berlin" pageId="8" pageNumber="130">Berlin</collectingRegion>
), one of the collectors of the 
<typeStatus box="[380,428,404,428]" pageId="8" pageNumber="130">type</typeStatus>
series.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
